cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.NE 

This paper deals with machine learning problems and strategies for dynamically increasing the effective sample size, which are topics that are commonly discussed in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
